{"tid":757811,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"屌那星今日去搭車去動物節 隔離個毒撚用漏聲耳筒聽歌","createTime":"2018-07-27T06:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T07:34:26.000Z","uid":14719,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"debf293def34bcc51754b14cd4aa207096d19e1f","tid":757811,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T06:45:15.000Z","msg":"見佢個樣正正常常<br />\n屌奶星 點知坐佢隔離<br />\n佢首先聽 only賣M巾 之後又播 Lisa刀劍首op<br />\n我個陣已經頂佢唔順想屌鳩佢<br />\n諗住仲有兩三個站頂埋<br />\n點知佢又係到聽奈葉op(應該係奈奈個首)同小圓OP<br />\n就黎落車個陣 我即刻忍唔住同佢講<br />\n先生，請問你聽撚夠你d毒歌未<br />\n佢即刻臉紅紅咁道歉熄聲<br />\n原來自己都知醜知自己聽毒歌既<br />\n利申聽開TL Hon同天堂雀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌 最後條死毒撚又係同我出埋同一個站"},{"pid":"73739b737838def466db18210e7ad7ba04097b43","tid":757811,"uid":35667,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T06:45:38.000Z","msg":"刀劍得罪你?"},{"pid":"439c3a57db04bb5bea5abf87a0aa5abb7d41e813","tid":757811,"uid":33868,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T06:45:45.000Z","msg":"你都咁清楚，咪又係一樣"},{"pid":"31c7f2e493ca41d2ab9d260f2b0d1126c3661371","tid":757811,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"439c3a57db04bb5bea5abf87a0aa5abb7d41e813","tid":757811,"uid":33868,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T06:45:45.000Z","msg":"你都咁清楚，咪又係一樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T06:46:21.000Z","msg":"我啲fd播過 啲旋律都有啲印象"},{"pid":"15030f21150623eba82e52e926687b91693bb643","tid":757811,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73739b737838def466db18210e7ad7ba04097b43","tid":757811,"uid":35667,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T06:45:38.000Z","msg":"刀劍得罪你?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T06:46:36.000Z","msg":"冇 對人不對事"},{"pid":"8f6bd97919e276bc6bbe230488cca5ce873ee418","tid":757811,"uid":2794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T06:47:32.000Z","msg":"樓主咪抄po！"},{"pid":"c5eae72b4a03c391d0fb5ded14bccf7be7edd51b","tid":757811,"uid":14719,"